title: 606. 10 Takeaways from Week 8
itunes:title: 606. 10 Takeaways from Week 8
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick ten storylines that stood out from Week 8 of the NFL season. To start off, the guys discuss how the Cowboys are a mess following their loss to the Eagles (1:07). Next, the trio look at the Vikings running the ball all over the Packers in a win (4:53). Later, the guys analyze the Dolphins flexing their muscles on the Rams in a victory and break down Dolphins QB Tua Tagovailoa's debut (14:22). To wrap up the show, DJ and Rhett talk about how the Broncos unlocked their offense in the second half to beat the Chargers in dramatic fashion (34:02). All that and more in this packed episode.
